<p>JEROMESVILLE (4/23/20)--We are excited to announce that the track at the stadium will be reopened for community use for walking/ jogging starting today. Please maintain social distancing and avoid congregating on the football field. Access and parking are available at the east end of the home bleachers.</p>
<p>The track was closed March 16, along with the buildings to students, in response to COVID-19.</p>
